<emphasis box="[290,507,1813,1836]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="24">Nervijuncta laffooni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, female (Brazil, São Paulo, Salesópolis). Terminalia, dorsal view. Ce1, basal segment of cercus; Ce2, distal segment of cercus; S8, sternite 8; T8, tergite 8; T9, tergite 9; T10, tergite 10; VF, vaginal furca.
